org.openwms.core.search

Class Tag

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.openwms.core.search.Tag
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    NounTag, VerbTag

    public class Tag
extends Object
implements Serializable
    A Tag represents a search keyword in the OpenWMS.org ActionSearch concept. Each Action consists of multiple Tags.
